<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Prayer in Times of Change</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Jan 15, 2017 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Gracious God,
</p>

 <p>
We live in a time of change, <br></br>
sometimes inspiring and exciting, <br></br>
sometimes distressing and frightening, <br></br>
but always challenging.
</p>

 <p>
Yet even in the midst of upheaval, <br></br>
we can be sure of this:
</p>

 <p>
The Father still loves us, <br></br>
the Son still calls us, <br></br>
The Spirit still leads us, <br></br>
and we must still follow â€“ <br></br></p>

 <p>
Together, <br></br>
one body, <br></br>
one faith.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


